name infwarerr
category Package
revision 77682
shortdesc Complete set of information/warning/error message macros
longdesc This package provides a complete set of macros for information,
longdesc warning and error messages. Under LaTeX, the commands are
longdesc wrappers for the corresponding LaTeX commands; under Plain TeX
longdesc they are available as complete implementations.
